DeprecatesObject.defineProperty()

Examples ofincorrectcode for this rule when used without exceptions:

/*eslint prefer-reflect: "error"*/

Object.defineProperty({}, 'foo', {value: 1})

Examples ofcorrectcode for this rule when used without exceptions:

/*eslint prefer-reflect: "error"*/

Reflect.defineProperty({}, 'foo', {value: 1})

Examples ofcorrectcode for this rule with the{ "exceptions": ["defineProperty"] }option:

/*eslint prefer-reflect: ["error", { "exceptions": ["defineProperty"] }]*/

Object.defineProperty({}, 'foo', {value: 1})
Reflect.defineProperty({}, 'foo', {value: 1})

